comment:
* Utility to create an instance of {@link ApfStats}.
     * @hide

methods.name: public Builder setDurationMs(long durationMs)
methods.comment: * Set the time interval in milliseconds these statistics covers.

methods.name: public Builder setReceivedRas(int receivedRas)
methods.comment: * Set the number of received RAs.

methods.name: public Builder setMatchingRas(int matchingRas)
methods.comment: * Set the number of received RAs matching a known RA.

methods.name: public Builder setDroppedRas(int droppedRas)
methods.comment: * Set the number of received RAs ignored due to the MAX_RAS limit.

methods.name: public Builder setZeroLifetimeRas(int zeroLifetimeRas)
methods.comment: * Set the number of received RAs with a minimum lifetime of 0.

methods.name: public Builder setParseErrors(int parseErrors)
methods.comment: * Set the number of received RAs that could not be parsed.

methods.name: public Builder setProgramUpdates(int programUpdates)
methods.comment: * Set the number of APF program updates from receiving RAs.

methods.name: public Builder setProgramUpdatesAll(int programUpdatesAll)
methods.comment: * Set the total number of APF program updates.

methods.name: public Builder setProgramUpdatesAllowingMulticast(int programUpdatesAllowingMulticast)
methods.comment: * Set the number of APF program updates from allowing multicast traffic.

methods.name: public Builder setMaxProgramSize(int maxProgramSize)
methods.comment: * Set the maximum APF program size advertised by hardware.
